						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged. It registers a gift of land at Kūttaṅguḍi, probably after purchasing it for 25 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold, for the maintenance of a perpetual lamp in the Tiruveṇkāḍudēvar, by [Mīna]vaṉ-Mahādēviyār a queen of Uttama-Chōḷa.</p>						

